g":"意外? 點意外先?<br />\n個套穿左?<br />\n食避孕藥拎錯胃仙U?<br />\n<br />\n唔係就收一收皮先<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a59f76015c6a083817b7199769b54bdb23bda328","tid":2344140,"uid":179729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T01:07:28.000Z","msg":"香港就犯法，大陸依啲無法為有法既地方就唔知了<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7b697a7c4f975945057b6cbb98fae61be644d0b","tid":2344140,"uid":40272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T01:09:02.000Z","msg":"第一個幾正 我都想同佢瘋狂生bb"},{"pid":"3f13080abdf8d87bab25a411d823ea2dff2268aa","tid":2344140,"uid":22553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"70b5039b9b7463840e877b3d7ee0998472e46e1e","tid":2344140,"uid":226622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T01:06:55.000Z","msg":"意外? 點意外先?<br />\n個套穿左?<br />\n食避孕藥拎錯胃仙U?<br />\n<br />\n唔係就收一收皮先<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T01:16:19.000Z","msg":"比契家佬搞大個肚咪叫意外囉"},{"pid":"0a9acac6f5c44639678136c4efa9ea397f252041","tid":2344140,"uid":303530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4f1ac475c78ac942ee857a3acf8bb75841409651","tid":2344140,"uid":39316,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T14:09:49.000Z","msg":"岩岩生完2個月又中出<br />\n應該話佢無意識避孕好，定有意識唔避孕好?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T01:16:21.000Z","msg":"聽佢鳩up啦 呢啲嘢邊撚到有意外<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3058ea3e18aab125a1c7a78fe1e03cd6a79121d","tid":2344140,"uid":123606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T01:27:30.000Z","msg":"香港就勞工處同平機會見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n中國就<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bc202cc0132deda739f7403ef0593dba939869e","tid":23